cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with sentiment analysis and natural language processing.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel method to integrate commonsense knowledge in a neural model.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the proposed model uses a gated attention mechanism to interface context representations with knowledge.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with extracting and selecting relevant knowledge paths from a knowledge resource.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the importance of understanding human needs and emotions in the context of machine learning and AI.
